node.text:
📍Niagara Falls

The ecosystems of the Niagara River are home to a plethora of protected and endangered animal species in New York, including the lake sturgeon fish!

🎥: Stanislav Moroz

#NiagaraFalls #Niagara #waterfall
Wow  The more beautiful it looks, the more dangerous it is, but this nature is a very beautiful sight.❤️❤️
I’ve always wanted to visit here. It looks so breathtaking!
Niagara falls is so wonderful! Amazing place😍
I've never seen the Falls from this vantage point; that's amazing
